# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:415
msgid "Effects"
msgstr "التأثيرات"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:416
msgid ""
"In addition to the many clip properties which can be animated and adjusted, "
"you can also drop an effect directly onto a clip from the effects dock. Each "
"effect is represented by a small colored letter icon. Clicking the effect "
"icon will populate the properties of that effect, and allow you to edit (and "
"animate) them. For the full list of effects, see :ref:`effects_ref`."
msgstr ""
"بالإضافة إلى العديد من خصائص المقطع التي يمكن تحريكها وتعديلها، يمكنك أيضًا "
